# rr-nav-link

Navigation link to be used with routerating. This component is used as a child
of `rr-nav-bar`. This component contains a `li` component with a
`stencil-route-link` inside.

| `url` _(required)_ | `url`     | The relative URL where this should link to. | `string` | `undefined` |
